title: Order relative to procedures to be followed when considering the Fiscal Year 2026 General Appropriations Bill

abstracts.abstract: Senate, May 5, 2025 -- (Filed by Mr. Rodrigues) Order relative to procedures to be followed when considering the House Bill making appropriations for the fiscal year 2026 for the maintenance of the departments, boards, commissions, institutions, and certain activities of the Commonwealth, for interest, sinking fund, and serial bond requirements, and for certain permanent improvements.
